    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Does Travel sickness\nspoil your journey?\nAvomine\nfor the prevention of land, sea and air travel\nsickness. Simply take Avomine at bedtime\nfor round the clock control.\nPHARMACY - ONLY MEDICINE\nAvomine\nNEVER LEAVE HOME WITHOUT IT\nEach Avomine tablet contains 25mg Promethazine theoclate BP.\nM\u0026B\nMay \u0026 Baker\nP.O. Box 35060 Naenae,\nLower Hutt\nNew Zealand\nCAUTION: Do not use during\npregnancy without medical direction.\nDo not drive a motor vehicle or\noperate machinery within 6-8 hours\nafter taking this medicine.",
      "FOR YOUR CONVENIENCE\nIN THE EVENT OF\nAIR SICKNESS\nCLOSE BY FOLDING\nCALL CABIN ATTENDANT FOR DISPOSAL."
